.

.

.
Oh and if ur getting those "promotion" bot spam comments make sure to check out my latest youtube vid addressing the issue!
.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sam Yang on July 22, 2021. May be an illustration of 1 person.

node.text:
Did some style study recently, practice video on my patreon! I focused on the Disney shape language in tangled, love the flow and expressiveness of their characters and thought it'd be cool to learn how they do it by trying to replicate things for myself! Rapunzel is the ref! 💛
.
I love art bc theres always more to learn 🥲
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
#characterdesign #characterart #characterconcept #characterillustration #digitalart #digitalillustration #digitalpainting #painting #illustration #drawing #artstyle #procreate #ipadpro #procreateart #procreateillustration
